###

### GET all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Accept: application/json

###

### GET one user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### POST create a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "patientName": "Jane Doe",
  "company": "HealthCorp",
  "position": "Patient",
